  <body>
    <segment id="1" parent="9" relname="span">Unfortunately, the Dutch animal shelters fill to the brim with homeless animals every summer</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="1" relname="elaboration">
Animals that have been dine away with by their owner for whatever reason and that are now left to their destiny.</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="13" relname="span">
It is in your name we ask their help.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="11" relname="solutionhood">
Because to improve the existence of these animals,</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="11" relname="span">
there is of course a need of money.</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="10" relname="list">
For vaccinations and sterilisations.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="10" relname="list">
For increase of the number of shelters.</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="10" relname="list">
For extra medical cate when necessary.</segment>
<group id="9" type="span" parent="3" relname="circumstance" />
